snippet.title: Ninja Kidz: Time Masters - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Ninja Kidz:cTime Masters is available now on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation, and PC via Steam, and coming to Xbox on October 20, 2023. Watch the latest trailer for another look at this action-adventure game.
